                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>In telegram 4178 from London, January 29, Ambassador Walter S. Gifford set forth
                    an analysis of differences between the United States and the United Kingdom
                    regarding policy in the Far East. It is scheduled for publication in volume
                    IV.</p>
